<br>
Shamans, Magicians, and Enchanters can cast Malo / Tash series spells which lower a target's resistances to different spells.  Chanters get their spell line at lvl 1.<br>
<br>
Otherwise, if you're attacking red mobs, make sure they are not 6 levels or more above you.  Untill lvl 32, you can't hit anything that's more than 6 levels above you.  From that point, the 1.2*(your level) rule starts to outpace the 6 level rule.  There's nothing that will get you around this. <p><center>
